
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Recycling";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="content-container p-4 bg-white shadow rounded">
        <h1 class="text-center text-success">Recycling</h1>

        <p>
            Within our own entity, we can assist with recycling directly in our own operations, ensuring we do our part.
            Recycling solutions contribute to an improved environment and climate, providing a positive outcome for the future.
        </p>

        <p>
            The recycling market in South Africa is growing into a sector with large potential. There is an increasing demand
            for high-quality secondary raw materials consisting of recycled plastics, paper, and glass.
        </p>

        <p>
            Recycling and reuse have a significant positive impact on the environment, including:
        </p>

        <ul class="custom-list">
            <li>✅ Reducing waste</li>
            <li>✅ Conserving resources</li>
            <li>✅ Protecting ecosystems</li>
            <li>✅ Reducing pollution</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            This project is also intended to optimize local capacity and facilities while contributing to long-term economic stability.
            Several potential sectors demonstrate that recycling is both socially and financially feasible.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div id="recyclingCarousel" class="carousel slide mt-4" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#recyclingCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#recyclingCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1"></button>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/Picture7.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Recycling Bins">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/Picture8.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Plastic Recycling">
            </div>
        </div>

        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#recyclingCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#recyclingCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
        </button>
    </div>
</div>

@section scripts {
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $('#recyclingCarousel').carousel();
        });
    </script>
}

<style>
    .content-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .custom-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

        .custom-list li {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #0275d8;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }

    .carousel-item img {
        height: 400px;
        object-fit: cover;
    }
</style>

<br/> 
